WEBVTT

00:08.299 --> 00:10.260
<i>Previously on</i> Why Women Kill..

00:10.343 --> 00:12.137
You can cheat on your wife
all you want,

00:12.220 --> 00:13.763
but you're not
touching mine.

00:13.847 --> 00:15.432
I am in love with you.

00:15.515 --> 00:17.225
You knew the rules.
I will never...

00:17.308 --> 00:18.560
leave my wife.

00:18.643 --> 00:20.103
So I can tell Rob is still mad

00:20.186 --> 00:21.104
about the other night.

00:21.187 --> 00:22.564
He hasn't called in days.

00:22.647 --> 00:25.734
Why would he even be with me
if he was so happy with her?

00:25.817 --> 00:27.318
<i>Maybe she did
something to hurt him</i>

00:27.402 --> 00:29.487
<i>and he needs time
to forgive her.</i>

00:29.571 --> 00:31.281
This project
I've been involved with,

00:31.364 --> 00:33.283
it's almost over.
I'll be home in time for dinner.

00:33.366 --> 00:34.242
Every night.

00:34.325 --> 00:36.327
It's Hector.

00:36.411 --> 00:38.121
He was the best hairdresser
I ever had.

00:38.204 --> 00:41.124
I've known for some time
about Karl's indiscretions.

00:41.207 --> 00:45.420
I saw his car parked
at some seedy motel.

00:47.046 --> 00:49.257
What in God's name?

00:49.340 --> 00:50.633
We haven't seen each
other in years.

00:50.717 --> 00:52.635
Hector was the only person

00:52.719 --> 00:54.596
who ever saw me
for the man I truly am.

00:54.679 --> 00:57.849
Stop romanticizing
your grubby little fling.

00:57.932 --> 00:59.267
Do you love him?

00:59.350 --> 01:00.643
I do.

01:00.727 --> 01:01.811
- Hey.
- Hmm?

01:01.895 --> 01:02.979
You fell asleep.

01:03.062 --> 01:04.439
- Take this.
- Uh...

01:04.522 --> 01:05.565
I don't think I should.

01:06.691 --> 01:07.859
<i>While I was away,</i>

01:07.942 --> 01:09.027
did you two fuck?

01:09.110 --> 01:12.030
We absolutely fucked.

01:12.113 --> 01:13.239
Okay.

01:13.323 --> 01:14.491
This was bound to happen, right?

01:14.574 --> 01:16.826
Since we're
all together now.

01:16.910 --> 01:18.495
All right, let's talk
about my script.

01:18.578 --> 01:20.872
I'm expecting offers in
the high six-figure range.

01:22.123 --> 01:24.334
Be good to Jade.
She's your muse.

01:24.417 --> 01:26.669
His muse?
I am the one who spent

01:26.753 --> 01:30.590
the last two years cleaning up
the mess he made of our lives.

01:30.673 --> 01:32.383
- What did he do?
- What didn't he do?

01:32.467 --> 01:33.885
Speed, cocaine.

01:33.968 --> 01:35.970
He's an addict.

01:36.054 --> 01:38.139
One of the producers
wants a rewrite.

01:38.223 --> 01:40.725
And if I can get it to them
on time, then... I'm back.

01:40.809 --> 01:43.311
And the money that will follow,
Jade, I can take care of you.

02:55.341 --> 02:57.927
